          <placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-1749" type="camp">camp</placeName>
        <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-483" type="subject">prisoners´</term> brigade accompanied by an <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-691" type="subject">orchestra</term></p>
