      <p>A passage through 'Frauenlager' [<placeName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_camps-1749" type="camp">Women's
          Camp]</placeName> to the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-541" type="subject">execution</term> square. <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-824" type="subject">Children</term> and <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-825" type="subject">women</term> hiding under the barracks... (June 1943)</p>
      <p><persName ref="#ehri_ts_porath_zeev">Zeev Porath</persName></p>
      <pb n="3" facs="EHRI-TS-19430000-A_03.jpg"/>
      <p> 'Dance of the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-895" type="subject">rabbis</term>'in the morning when the brigade is leaving for work... (<date when="1943-04">April 1943</date>)</p>
      <p><persName ref="#ehri_ts_porath_zeev">Zeev Porath</persName></p>
